41:30.622 --> 41:34.560
The, um... The retreat where
you found me, has a mantra.

41:34.593 --> 41:35.894
Do you know what it is?

41:35.927 --> 41:39.598
"In silence
the universe answers?"

41:39.631 --> 41:41.767
There's more to it.

41:41.800 --> 41:43.935
"In silence
the universe answers,

41:43.969 --> 41:47.639
